## Trading Autonomy

| Tier | Credit range | Action |
|------|-------------|--------|
| 1 | < {{tier1Threshold}} credits | Auto-execute, no notification |
| 2 | {{tier1Threshold}}–{{tier2Threshold}} credits | Execute, then notify owner |
| 3 | > {{tier2Threshold}} credits | Ask owner before executing |

**Reserve floor**: Never auto-spend below {{reserveFloor}} credits.
**If balance hits floor**: Increase sharing priority, pause non-essential spending, notify owner.

